sentences: Ine Kristine Hoem (born 19 December 1985 in Oslo, Norway) is a Norwegian jazz singer and the daughter of the author Edvard Hoem.
Hoem got her music diploma from the Jazz program at Norwegian University of Science and Technology (2009).
Within the band PELbO, she released the album PELbO (2010) and  Days Of Trancendence (2011).
